race.comment: KEEP ROLLING (2) hit the ground running from the squeeze draw with a strong early split last time, paving the way for a 1.3 lengths win at Sandown over 515m in 29.22. Got the money at his only try from this box. Well placed and can measure up. ULTIMATE WARRIOR (8) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 4 length second (34.42) over 595m at Sandown. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Can measure up. LOCHINVAR NUGGET (1) tends to take a while to wind up, missing the placings two back but running on to last time finishing second (28.46) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Was a winner at his only start from this draw. Bold showing expected. WHITE CREST (6) boasts a solid strike-rate from this box.
